{"tid":5360,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港民族黨：青年新政根本從沒有主張過「香港獨立」！","createTime":"2016-11-27T00:04:09.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-27T01:43:33.000Z","uid":28114,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"766e49d7eb58f7c7294a34741273e549f924d44b","tid":5360,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T00:04:09.000Z","msg":"香港民族黨陳浩天出聲明回應前港督彭定康的談話，聲明內裏批評青年新政：青年新政根本從沒有主張過「香港獨立」！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"> Youngspiration has never, for its entire existence, ever advocated for Hong Kong independence.</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hknationalparty/posts/571933033005655?pnref=story\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhknationalparty%2Fposts%2F571933033005655%3Fpnref%3Dstory&d=Pkv6XM7ghmIAJTpJxxntuMW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=f05c43f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hknationalparty/posts/571933033005655?pnref=story</a>"},{"pid":"8879528f5421790b4a8ed0972a3e04a9edae4676","tid":5360,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T00:05:58.000Z","msg":"部分傳媒查詢民族黨就前港督彭定康是日（11/25）對香港獨立之相關言論，敝黨回應如下：<br />\n<br />\n1. 彭定康指「應重回討論政府管治同民主的問題，而非討論香港獨立」，民族黨重申若香港人無香港主權，就不會有真正的民主，政府管治亦只會完全由中國政府操控。追求獨立正是追求民主、自由、人權的表現，任何一個文明國家均不會容忍共產黨此等法西斯癌瘤繼續滋長。<br />\n<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: red;\">青年新政由始至終均無主張香港獨立</span>，彭以「學生遊戲」形容梁游二人之言行，以此與所有香港獨立的支持者掛勾，並套用至香港本土運動、甚至整個獨立運動，上述說法未免以偏概全，民族黨對此表示遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n3. 彭離開香港多年，縱間中有返港訪問或出席公開場合，惟香港社會十九年間各方面包括民主、民生等問題急劇惡化，恐彭未能適應並察覺當中變化。另外，彭指喪失「2014年建立的道德高地」的講法，民族黨認為如香港人空有道德高地，卻無法擺脫中國殖民的客觀現實，則彭的講法是漠視香港人被殖民壓迫的慘況。<br />\n<br />\n4. 今日中國的角色如同當年的納粹德國，香港人追求脫離極權的道德正當性理據充份，而反殖民更是廿一世紀文明社會的共識，民族黨尊重彭當年捍衛港人民主，勇於對抗中國政府，如彭關注香港民主發展，則應向國際社會表達中國對香港的殖民現況，不應重蹈綏靖政策的歷史教訓。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hknationalparty/posts/571434059722219\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhknationalparty%2Fposts%2F571434059722219&d=Pkv6XM7ghmIAJTpJxxntuMW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=26d625c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hknationalparty/posts/571434059722219</a>"},{"pid":"9268bc402fec2f8791425305926d652824e394a1","tid":5360,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T00:07:09.000Z","msg":"等睇本民青死兜爛兜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f35c2cc04ea6a6809f3d1a69d9507b740a99c3a2","tid":5360,"uid":7026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T00:23:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ba4fee2a14a6e35e9d576698743a56283c5edeb","tid":5360,"uid":1096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T00:28:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b50275ec98b3cbc2886ee723bf0a45d86c422cb0","tid":5360,"uid":22068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T00:34:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>等睇本民青死兜爛兜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢邊好似唔準講本民青壞話，否則自動變五毛打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76ca124789a72f579ad833068b882bb5f4f5fc64","tid":5360,"uid":6238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T00:37:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>等睇本民青死兜爛兜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢邊好似唔準講本民青壞話，否則自動變五毛打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n本民青果班垃圾死去膠登啦"},{"pid":"8f2423b0cd7076f4bf02ce2841c9096ed31e7d7b","tid":5360,"uid":19211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T00:39:03.000Z","msg":"做勢大會黃俊傑有講過，好似係"},{"pid":"6ff91fcd188c9ebaeec8fd25c564408150879c15","tid":5360,"uid":25350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T01:17:52.000Z","ms